item.title: Norah Jones - Don't Know Why - Ukulele Cheats
item.description: Play along video for the song Don't Know Why by Norah Jones from the channel Ukulele Cheats. Chords used in the song: A♯7, A♯maj7, C7, Daug, D♯, F, F6, F7, Gm7.

item.title: Norah Jones - Come Away With Me - Key of Am - Cynthia Lin Music
